#: ../../../index.rst:7
msgid "Welcome to discord.py"
msgstr "歡迎使用 discord.py"

#: ../../../index.rst:12
msgid ""
"discord.py is a modern, easy to use, feature-rich, and async ready API "
"wrapper for Discord."
msgstr ""
"discord.py 是一個現代、易於使用、功能豐富且支援異步的 Discord API 包裝器。"

#: ../../../index.rst:15
msgid "**Features:**"
msgstr "**功能：**"

#: ../../../index.rst:17
msgid "Modern Pythonic API using ``async``\\/``await`` syntax"
msgstr "使用 ``async``\\/``await`` 語法的現代 Pythonic API"

#: ../../../index.rst:18
msgid "Sane rate limit handling that prevents 429s"
msgstr "合理的速率限制處理機制，防止 429 錯誤"

#: ../../../index.rst:19
msgid "Command extension to aid with bot creation"
msgstr "用於協助機器人開發的命令擴充功能"

#: ../../../index.rst:20
msgid "Easy to use with an object oriented design"
msgstr "物件導向設計，易於使用"

#: ../../../index.rst:21
msgid "Optimised for both speed and memory"
msgstr "在速度與記憶體使用上皆經過最佳化"

